profile:
At Buehler Custom Woodworking, we believe in Craftsmanship, Integrity and Design.  Our millwork reflects our commitment to you, our customer.  Call us and let's discuss your vision.  It is our goal to make your personal style and ideas come to life.  

We offer our clients a wide variety of products including custom kitchen and cabinetry, built-in wall units, bathroom vanities and more. 

Our shop includes a fully equipped millwork department, professional spray booth and assembly area.

We custom blend and apply all of our finishes using only the best products and procedures.  Our finishes are available in any colour and any style to suit your needs.
